reviews.review_text: Sick show.  Sick aud copy. yum yum
- All in all a good show. Nice sound! Sweet peak during Stella.
Nice 2nd Set Highlights: Stella Blue, It's All Over Now, Baby Blue

Love this one The sound here is real nice to my ears. I chose this one again today not because of Charlie Miller but because it looked like the latest version put up here. Over the years have listened to this show at lease a dozen times. Always loved the 2nd set. Stranger Scarlet Fire is hot along with Estimated Eyes. and the rest of the set too for that matter. 
 Gets 4 stars from me only 4 cause the 5 star rating is for the above and beyond shows . This one is close but not like the 78 Oregon show with close encounters. To me that's a 5... 
 As a kid still in high school we would all swap tapes and this is one of last ones I got before jumping in with both feet the following year on tour.
So Few Reviews! On any of the versions, very strange.  This show smokes and has that added Merry Prankster vibe.  Love it!
Good show Good quality Audience tape.  Best stuff includes The Other One and Stella Blue.  Thanks Charlie Miller for your never-ending fountain of music.
